  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX at 6592.91 sitting just below the massive +8445.1M gamma wall at 6605, dealers are positioned to aggressively sell any push higher toward that level while providing strong support on dips toward the 6600 (+7344.9M) and 6500 (-4512.4M) strikes. The PIN regime with 8937.1M total GEX creates a powerful mean-reversion setup, with dealers acting as liquidity providers who will fade moves in either direction. Key levels to watch are the 6605 max gamma strike as resistance and 6500 as the critical support level where dealer behavior flips from stabilizing to amplifying.\n\n**Bottom line:** expect the market to get pinned between 6500-6605 with dealers capping upside moves.",
